{"tid":1155731,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"香港樂壇以死，新出道都走去拍劇","createTime":"2019-05-15T06:50:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T07:59:46.000Z","uid":239829,"like":3,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a23cbb07163af988dcef03ec8956f55cf9205e2d","tid":1155731,"uid":239829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:50:01.000Z","msg":"曾樂彤啱啱由歌手出道唔夠兩年，未有成名既音樂作品，就已經被ViuTV搵咗去拍PTU呢部大製作。如果佢靠呢套劇紅咗，遲D一定大把人搵佢去拍戲，唔使旨意再聽佢唱歌。<br />\n<br />\n好似鄭中基，張繼聰，張衛健呢D都係樂壇出身，但因為拍戲拍劇紅咗所以就少咗甚至無再唱歌。可能有D唱歌並唔係太有實力或者多Fans所以先走去拍戲。但事實就係拍戲拍劇比唱歌好搵好多。而家就算係香港真係有實力同真心鐘意唱歌既歌手，都會好似GEM咁返大陸搵食。<br />\n<br />\n係咪個個香港歌手都真心鐘意唱歌就見仁見智。而家香港樂壇搵唔到食，就算新出道既歌手都走去拍戲拍劇，好難專心唱歌。"},{"pid":"ce6f2d0bb860af8fb3954db0731979e9528cbbf2","tid":1155731,"uid":68678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"曾樂彤唔再唱歌真係要多謝viutv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58d07c72ded75d1bcf7aec4de19b80cc0219d6aa","tid":1155731,"uid":239829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6f2d0bb860af8fb3954db0731979e9528cbbf2","tid":1155731,"uid":68678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"曾樂彤唔再唱歌真係要多謝viutv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04c0073feadd430f0e2db632d60ad6f23fae78d8","tid":1155731,"uid":239829,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce6f2d0bb860af8fb3954db0731979e9528cbbf2","tid":1155731,"uid":68678,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T06:51:28.000Z","msg":"曾樂彤唔再唱歌真係要多謝viutv<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" 